gantt
%% Gantt Chart Example - Trimble Theme
%%
%% Theme Impact:
%% - Task bars: taskBkgColor (#0063A3 Trimble Blue) with white text
%% - Active tasks: activeTaskBkgColor (#FBAD26 Trimble Gold) - highlights current work
%% - Done tasks: doneTaskBkgColor (#349C44 Trimble Green) - shows completion
%% - Critical tasks: critBkgColor (#B44E2A Trimble Brown) - emphasizes critical path
%% - Milestones: Diamond markers using primaryColor
%% - Today line: todayLineColor (#FBAD26 Trimble Gold) vertical marker
%% - Section backgrounds: Alternating sectionBkgColor (#DCEDF9, #E0ECCF, #FFF5E4)
%% - Grid lines: lineColor for time axis
%% - Labels: textColor for dates and task names
%% - Layout: barHeight 20px, barGap 4px, axisFormat %Y-%m-%d
    title Project Development Timeline
    dateFormat YYYY-MM-DD
    excludes weekends

    section Planning
    Requirements Gathering     :done,    req, 2024-01-01, 2w
    System Design             :done,    design, after req, 2w
    Architecture Review       :done,    review, after design, 3d

    section Development
    Backend API Development   :active,  api, 2024-01-29, 4w
    Database Schema           :done,    db, 2024-01-29, 1w
    Frontend Development      :         fe, after db, 4w
    Integration               :         int, after api, 2w

    section Testing
    Unit Testing              :         unit, after db, 5w
    Integration Testing       :         inttest, after int, 2w
    UAT                       :         uat, after inttest, 1w

    section Deployment
    Staging Deployment        :         staging, after uat, 3d
    Production Deployment     :crit,    prod, after staging, 2d
    Post-Launch Support       :         support, after prod, 1w

    section Milestones
    MVP Ready                 :milestone, mvp, 2024-03-01, 0d
    Go Live                   :milestone, golive, 2024-03-20, 0d
